## Data Attributes

| Attribute | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `data-message-complete="true"` | AI done streaming |
| `data-state="open\|closed"` | Collapsible state |
| `data-testid="*"` | Element selection |

### Enhance-Transcribe Selectors

| Element | Selector |
|---|---|
| Hidden file input | `[data-testid="hidden-file-input"]` |
| Idle screen | `[data-testid="upload-or-record-screen"]` |
| Start Recording button | `[data-testid="upload-or-record-start-recording"]` |
| Recording screen | `[data-testid="active-recording-screen"]` |
| Stop Recording button | `[data-testid="active-recording-stop"]` |
| Setup screen | `[data-testid="transcription-setup-screen"]` |
| Start Transcription button | `[data-testid="transcription-setup-start"]` |
| Result screen | `[data-testid="transcription-result-screen"]` |
| Heading | `[data-testid="transcribe-heading"]` |
| Benchmark callout | `[data-testid="accuracy-benchmark-callout"]` |
| File error notice | `[data-testid="inline-file-error-notice"]` |
| Leave guard "Stay" | button "Stay on page" |
| Leave guard "Leave" | button "Leave anyway" |
| Completion signal | button "Transcribe another file" |
